contentrichtext.text: {{Infobox city Japan |Name= Nagasu |JapaneseName= 長洲町 |settlement_type= Town |MapImage= Nagasu in Kumamoto Prefecture.png |Region= [[Kyūshū]] |Prefecture=[[Kumamoto Prefecture|Kumamoto]] |District= [[Tamana District, Kumamoto|Tamana]] |Area_km2= 19.43 |PopDate= 2003 |Population= 17,683 |Density_km2= auto |Coords= |LatitudeDegrees= 32 |LatitudeMinutes= 56 |LatitudeSeconds= |LongtitudeDegrees= 130 |LongtitudeMinutes= 27 |LongtitudeSeconds= |Tree= |Flower= |Bird= |SymbolImage= |SymbolDescription= |Mayor= |CityHallPostalCode= |CityHallAddress= |CityHallPhone= |CityHallLink= [http://www.town.nagasu.lg.jp/ Town of Nagasu] }} {{nihongo|'''Nagasu'''|長洲町|Nagasu-machi}} is a [[towns of Japan|town]] located in [[Tamana District, Kumamoto|Tamana District]], [[Kumamoto Prefecture|Kumamoto]], [[Japan]]. As of 2003, the town has an estimated [[population]] of 17,683 and the [[population density|density]] of 910.09 persons per km². The total area is 19.43 km². ==External links == {{Commons category-inline}} *[http://www.town.nagasu.lg.jp/ Nagasu official website] {{ja icon}} [[Category:Towns in Kumamoto Prefecture]] {{Kumamoto-geo-stub}}
